{"id":1178,"date":"2018-08-02T15:00:44","date_gmt":"2018-08-02T19:00:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=professeur&#038;p=1178"},"modified":"2023-08-17T13:53:03","modified_gmt":"2023-08-17T17:53:03","slug":"corinne-roland","status":"publish","type":"professeur","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/equipe\/corinne-roland\/","title":{"rendered":"Corinne Roland"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Originaire de Vancouver, Corinne Roland a \u00e9tudi\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019Universit\u00e9 de Colombie-Britannique (UBC) o\u00f9 elle a obtenu un baccalaur\u00e9at en g\u00e9ographie urbaine.\u00a0\u00a0Elle a ensuite poursuivi ses \u00e9tudes par un baccalaur\u00e9at en enseignement primaire et secondaire.\u00a0\u00a0Puis elle a compl\u00e9t\u00e9 ses \u00e9tudes \u00e0 l\u2019universit\u00e9 McGill en d\u00e9crochant une maitrise en linguistique appliqu\u00e9e.\u00a0Finalement elle s\u2019est install\u00e9e \u00e0 Montr\u00e9al. Elle y a travaill\u00e9 dans plusieurs c\u00e9geps avant d\u2019adopter le n\u00f4tre.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":6703,"template":"","categorie-equipe":[202],"departement-equipe":[283,282],"specialite-equipe":[],"etiquette-interne":[],"class_list":["post-1178","professeur","type-professeur","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorie-equipe-personnel-enseignant","departement-equipe-anglais","departement-equipe-langues"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur\/1178","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/professeur"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/6703"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1178"}],"wp:term":[{"ta